     C                   MOVE      *BLANK        MsgIDXAr
     C                   MOVE      *BLANK        MsgDtaXAr
     C                   Z-ADD     0             Idx
     C                   Z-ADD     0             WIdx
 
      ** Validation
      ** Validate Report foreign Source Income
     C                   IF        (DDRFSI <> 'Y') AND (DDRFSI <> 'N')
     C                   EVAL      DDRFSIOK = 'N'
     C                   EVAL      Idx = Idx + 1
     C                   EVAL      FldNamXAr(Idx) = 'DDRFSI'
